<F P=106> [Announcer-read report over video] </F>
  [Excerpt] The cross-border operations launched by the 
security forces south of Hakkari's Cukurca District on 12 April 
against terrorists trying to infiltrate into Turkey are 
continuing. The Shivi, Mezi, and Keryaderi camps used by the 
terrorists as bases in Northern Iraq have been captured. The 
weapons in these camps have been brought to Cukurca and shown to 
the press. [passage omitted] 

