Material From East"] 
  [Text] Brussels, 13 Apr 94 (AGENCE EUROPE) -- The Council 
of the European Union [EU] gave the following response to 
written question No. E-3697/93 by Mr A. Smith: "The Council does 
not have information on contraband trade in nuclear material, 
