traffic into the European Union of nuclear and/or radioactive 
material from the Central and East European countries and the 
former Soviet Union. In this context, the Commission is 
currently preparing a communication to the Council which should 
make it possible to get a better idea of the scope of this 
problem as well as action which could be taken at Community 
level in terms of information." 

