  [Text] Hamburg, April 16 (CTK) -- Czech Defense Minister 
Antonin Baudys, on a short visit to the north German city of 
Hamburg, and his German counterpart Volker Ruehe today agreed on 
carrying out a joint military exercise, the two ministers told 
journalists at a joint news conference. 
