<H4>    Calls For UN-EU-U.S.-Russian Team on Bosnia </H4>

<F P=102> BR2004091494 Brussels LE SOIR in French 19 Apr 94 p 6 </F>
<F P=103> BR2004091494 </F>
<F P=104>  Brussels LE SOIR </F>
<F P=105>  French </F>


