  From there, from Croatia, some of them will go to the 
Bosnian 
towns of Dracevo, Mostar, and Medjugorje, and the logistics 
group will go on to the Croatian town of Divulje. 
  This is the fourth and most numerous group of blue helmets 
belonging to the Cordoba Group to leave for Bosnia-Herzegovina 
