<F P=100> SPAIN </F>
<H3> <TI>   Barcelona Military Governor's Office Attacked </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Barcelona Military Governor's Office Attacked </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1804134094 Madrid Teletexto TVE in Spanish 1322 GMT 18 Apr 
94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1804134094 </F>
<F P=104>  Madrid Teletexto TVE </F>
<F P=105>  Spanish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Excerpt] One dead and 12 injured after two grenades, fired 
at the office of the military governor of Barcelona, exploded 
early this afternoon. The police attribute the attack to Basque 
Fatherland and Liberty [ETA]. [passage omitted] 

</TEXT>

