  [Text] Prosperity Party deputy leader Abdullah Gul has said 
that even if it has to act alone, Turkey must violate the arms 
embargo imposed on the Bosnian Muslims. 
  At a news conference in parliament, Abdullah Gul said that 
the weapons of the former Yugoslavia are now in the hands of 
