<H3> <TI>   Aho Offers Good Offices in Russia-Estonia Talks </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Aho Offers Good Offices in Russia-Estonia Talks </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1904202394 Helsinki Radio Finland in English 1900 GMT 19 
