<F P=104>  Hamburg BILD </F>
<F P=105>  German </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [Unattributed report: "Intelligence Service Murder: Wife </F>
Trampled to Death"] 
  [Text] The murder of the German intelligence service man 
in Libya is becoming increasingly mysterious! BILD heard: 
Before his death, brutally slain Silvian Becker was in a coma 
for four weeks. His wife was trampled to death. The German 
Embassy only heard of the deed 14 days later. The latest 
speculation in Bonn is that the Beckers were slain by Libyan 
agents because they had been on the trail of 25 Germans who 
produce poison gas for al-Qadhdhafi. 

