<H3> <TI>   Kliridhis, Papandreou Discuss UN Efforts </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Kliridhis, Papandreou Discuss UN Efforts </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC2104070494 Nicosia Cyprus Broadcasting Corporation Radio 
Network in Greek 0430 GMT 21 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> NC2104070494 </F>
<F P=104>  Nicosia Cyprus Broadcasting Corporation Radio 
